764
00:39:35,348 --> 00:39:36,188
Mingzhi.

765
00:39:37,748 --> 00:39:38,588
Thank you.

766
00:39:39,468 --> 00:39:41,388
Xiao Zhongwu, as the commander-in-chief,

767
00:39:41,788 --> 00:39:42,828
was reckless,

768
00:39:43,227 --> 00:39:45,147
leading our troops into an ambush.

769
00:39:45,428 --> 00:39:46,507
He was too proud

770
00:39:47,027 --> 00:39:48,388
to seek prompt rescue,

771
00:39:48,948 --> 00:39:51,667
