775
00:39:57,428 --> 00:39:58,268
Huaijin.

776
00:39:58,948 --> 00:39:59,868
I broke my promise.

777
00:40:01,268 --> 00:40:02,108
Sorry.

778
00:40:04,428 --> 00:40:06,147
