797
00:41:11,468 --> 00:41:12,308
Yeah.

798
00:41:12,507 --> 00:41:13,347
No misunderstandings.

799
00:41:14,107 --> 00:41:14,947
In the end,

800
00:41:15,827 --> 00:41:16,667
